Robin L. Marino

Age : 62Public asset : 311,800 USDLinked companies :  Summer Infant, Inc. 





Summary 



Ms. Robin L. Marino is Chairman at Summer Infant, Inc. Ms. Marino was previously employed as President & Chief Executive Officer-Merchandising by Martha Stewart Living Omnimedia, Inc. and President & Chief Operating Officer by Kate Spade LLC.She also served on the board at Hampshire Group Ltd.She received her undergraduate degree from Stetson University.



